text: Laurence William Neal (born 18 July 1947) is an Australian politician. He is a member of the National Party. He served as a Senator for Victoria from 1980 to 1981. Neal was born in Wangaratta, Victoria. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Members of the Australian Senate Category:National Party of Australia politicians Category:Politicians from Victoria (Australia)
